Consider the following C program:


#include < stdio.h >  
int gate(int n) {  
    int d, t, newnum, turn;  
    newnum = turn = 0; t=1;  
    while(n >= t) t *= 10;  
    t /= 10;  
    while(t > 0) {  
        d = n / t;  
        n = n % t;  
        t /= 10;  
        if(turn) newnum = 10 * newnum + d;  
        turn = (turn + 1) % 2;  
    }  
    return newnum;  
}
